                <note rend="inline" type="source">881.00/1793a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-12-10T15:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 10, 1940—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3736. Please forward Department by telegraph text of statement made in House of
                    Commons by Butler on December 4 regarding Tangier and send copy to Tangier by
                    mail.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
